    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We have breakfast at the hotel and then wander down to the monetary to look around. It turns out it’s rather more ominous than it looks - having been used as a fort to fight off attackers, then being sold and used as a concentration camp a few hundred years ago. One cannot go in, but we peek through the door - arched roofs look good even dripping in blood. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
