      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We have lunch with an amazing view and do some admin that we’ve been putting off. With the lighter packs Cait comes up with a plan to do the last 100km to Santiago and get our certificate. We’re heading off to Pontevedra to meet Cait’s sister Coutnay, but will come back to Vigo after that and then walk to Santiago. ",
