      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "One car sick bus ride later, and a train that goes under water we arrive in Pontevedra. A beautiful city that feels a bit like Porto. We’ve treated ourselves to a nice apartment for the weekend. The last little rest before the final push to Santiago. The host of the house is incredibly sweet and genuine. ",
            "link": null
          },
