    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I’m exhausted, but am excited to eat some fresh leaves and vegetables, so I head off to the supermarket. Cait has a vendetta against the pine sap in our pants from yesterday. Cait looks into a yoga retreat for the time that I’m going to the Alps. I find some time to catch up on the last few days of writing. Courtnay lands safely in Santiago and will join us early tomorrow morning. GOOD NIGHT EVERYONE 😴 (I haven’t really got used to the late nights, with the time difference to Portugal it’s still light at 10:30pm and feels silly to go to bed before midnight).",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "I’m exhausted, but am excited to eat some fresh leaves and vegetables, so I head off to the supermarket. Cait has a vendetta against the pine sap in our pants from yesterday. Cait looks into a yoga retreat for the time that I’m going to the Alps. I find some time to catch up on the last few days of writing. Courtnay lands safely in Santiago and will join us early tomorrow morning. GOOD NIGHT EVERYONE 😴 (I haven’t really got used to the late nights, with the time difference to Portugal it’s still light at 10:30pm and feels silly to go to bed before midnight).",
