    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Courtnay arrives in the morning and we make some scrambled eggs along with a catchup. Then head off for a walk into town, buy a speedo (wear sunglasses around my pasty thighs) and look around. We stumble across a book festival where some young children are doing a reading competition - or so we think. We get a free churro with our coffee and head to the swimming hole (literally what people call it). Which is just a small beach next to the river with trees and grass. ",
            "link": null
          },
