          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Through the scorching heat of the day we wonder further along to a small cafe for lunch. It’s a smaller residential suburb. We enter in a pool of sweat and the waiter shows us utter ambivalence. A burger later and we head back towards our house for a siesta. ",
            "link": null
