          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "It’s been such a lovely visit with Courtnay - she’s on very much the same wavelength as us by way of relaxation first. We take the day very slowly. After a sleep we head off to dinner: tapas on the street. We try the local octopus delicacy, I can’t say that I’m such a fan. I feel sad eating octopus, having befriended one or two as a child in Knysna. ",
