          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We amble back towards home and come across a small bar with people in the street. An elderly drunk woman is talking passionately with a man, her old person wheeled basket at her side. As we pass her she lurches towards us and unleashes a growling snort with a demonic tone at us - we scream and laugh and continue walking. I’m uncertain as to what she meant to do, I’ve come up with the following options:",
